snippet.title: More Than "one way" Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
-More Than "one way" is a first person survival/puzzle horror game where you must piece together the past, and face your fears as the set falls apart around you.

-are you ready to remember?

Wishlist now on Steam:  
https://steampowered.com/app/2349570/
